  <brief_title>A Study of Lyrica as Treatment for Sleep Problems in Patients With Sleep Problems and Seizures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pregabalin BID Add-on Trial: a Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Parallel-Group Single-Center Sleep EEG Study in Patients With Partial Seizures and Sleep Disturbance Part B: a Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Parallel-Group Study of Pregabalin Add-on Treatment</official_title>
