    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Pfizer</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the effects of pregabalin on sleep problems in
      patients with seizures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
